  "What is the slope of a line through (1,2) and (3,6)?": "",
  "Slope = (y₂ - y₁) / (x₂ - x₁) = (6 - 2) / (3 - 1) = 4 / 2 = 2. The other options — '4', '1/2', and '3' — are related concepts but do not correctly answer this specific question.": ""
